el Comics)|Valkyrie / Scrapper 142]]\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Sorry to Bother You]]''\n| Detroit \n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Annihilation (film)|Annihilation]]''\n| Josie Radek\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Furlough (film)|Furlough]]''\n| Nicole Stevens\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Little Woods]]''\n| Ollie\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Dirty Computer]]''\n| Zen / Mary Apple 23\n| Short film\n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Creed II]]''\n| Bianca Taylor\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2019\n|''Brave Girl Rising''\n|Nasro (voice)\n|Short film\n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Avengers: Endgame]]''\n| Valkyrie\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Men in Black: International]]''\n| Molly Wright / Agent M\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Between Two Ferns: The Movie]]''\n| Herself\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Lady and the Tramp (2019 film)|Lady and the Tramp]]''\n| Lady (voice)\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n|2020\n|''[[Sylvie's Love]]''\n| Sylvie\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |<ref>{{Cite magazine|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/tessa-thompson-nnamdi-asomugha-star-period-drama-sylvie-1189115|title=Tessa Thompson, Nnamdi Asomugha to Star in Period Drama 'Sylvie' | last = Bitran | first = Tara |magazine=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Valence Media]]|location=Los Angeles, California|date=February 22, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2022\n| ''[[Thor: Love and Thunder]]''\n| Valkyrie\n|\n| style=\"text-align: center;\"  | <!-- Add refs to reliable source(s) here -->\n|-\n| TBA\n| ''[[Passing (film)|Passing]]''\n| Irene Redfield\n| Post-production\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref>{{cite web|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|url=https://deadline.com/2018/08/rebecca-hall-passing-movie-tessa-thompson-ruth-negga-nella-larsen-novel-1202440801/|title=Rebecca Hall To Make Directorial Debut With \u2018Passing\u2019; Tessa Thompson & Ruth Negga Star In Adaptation Of 1920s Novel|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|publisher=[[Penske Media Corporation]]|location=Los Angeles, California|date=August 6, 2018}}</ref> \n|}\n\n===Television===\n<!-- Please note: do NOT use \"rowspans\" per WP:FILMOGRAPHY -->\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n|2005\n|''[[Cold Case]]''\n|Wilhelmina \"Billie\" Doucette\n|Episode: \"Best Friends\"\n|-\n|2005\u20132006\n|''[[Veronica Mars]]''\n|[[Jackie Cook]]\n|Main role (12 episodes)\n|-\n| 2006\n|''[[Grey's Anatomy]]''\n|Camille Travis\n|2 episodes<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity/g22863194/greys-anatomy-cameos/?slide=4|title=34 Actors You Forgot Appeared on 'Grey's Anatomy'|last=Mitchell|first=Amanda|date=2018-09-06|website=Marie Claire|language=en-US|access-date=2019-03-27}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2006\n|''{{sortname|The|Initiation of Sarah|The Initiation of Sarah (2006 film)}}''\n|Esme\n|[[Television film]]\n|-\n|2007\n|''[[Hidden Palms]]''\n|Nikki Barnes\n|Main role (7 episodes)\n|-\n|2008\n|''[[Life (NBC TV series)|Life]]''\n|Liza\n|Episode: \"Trapdoor\"\n|-\n| 2009\n|''[[Mental (TV series)|Mental]]''\n|Lainey Jefferson\n|Episode: \"Lines in the Sand\"\n|-\n| 2009\n|''[[Private Practice (TV series)|Private Prac